.TH audio_player 1 "February 2026" "arma-tools" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
audio_player \- play OGG, WSS, and WAV audio files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B audio_player
.RI [ options ]
.I input.ogg|input.wss|input.wav
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B audio_player
plays supported audio files using miniaudio backends.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI "--backend " name
Force backend (pulse, alsa, wasapi, coreaudio, jack, null, default).
.TP
.BI "--device " name
Select playback device by case-insensitive substring match.
.TP
.B
--list-backends
List available audio backends and exit.
.TP
.B
--list-devices
List playback devices for the selected backend and exit.
.TP
.BR -h , " --help"
Show help.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR ogg_validate (1)
